{"tid":2405182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"非洲女商人販運1.4公斤冰毒 判囚24年","createTime":"2021-02-12T07:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T08:42:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"12d2b22f3cb943e568b87e0251e9c8a758a35d09","tid":2405182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"據庭上透露，女被告在還柙期間產子，按照懲教署規定，至其子4歲時將交由保良局照顧。法官陳慶偉指因案件涉及跨境因素，加刑兩年，但考慮到被告將與兒子骨肉分離，酌情減刑一年，終判囚24年。<br />\n<br />\n被告Estina Mukasera（31歲）早前被裁定在2018年8月3日在機場入境大堂販運危險藥物、即約1.4公斤冰毒。案情透露，被告當時以朱古力包裝紙掩飾。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉判刑時指，案件牽涉國際販毒圖利的跨境因素，須加重刑罰，決定加刑兩年；但被告在還柙期間誕子，兒子在4歲時會送交保良局照顧，考慮被告在服刑期間會離開親生骨肉，酌情減刑一年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/4PTJU5B45BHBTB73V6MXMR7CZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2F4PTJU5B45BHBTB73V6MXMR7CZE%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=54a2416a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2F4PTJU5B45BHBTB73V6MXMR7CZE%2F&h=9c3dd44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/4PTJU5B45BHBTB73V6MXMR7CZE/</a>"},{"pid":"f556a433218791689c3f9ec7fbdbae54e3b74e2f","tid":2405182,"uid":76804,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hYMU11j_SVgAI96w1N-ZhswvFME=/filters:quality(100)/d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/05-27-2020/t_8c328e44e4fd4c91b43bc037d0d565ab_name_1590605514_a6d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhYMU11j_SVgAI96w1N-ZhswvFME%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F05-27-2020%2Ft_8c328e44e4fd4c91b43bc037d0d565ab_name_1590605514_a6d5.jpg&h=905ce127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">警二代涉販毒3kg 律政司撤控</span>"},{"pid":"9b8038f4d7d6d6de956eccc39496713e05f90fec","tid":2405182,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislik